text:
I like this mall!
It's def my number 1 choice of malls to visit with in a reasonable distance from where I live (followed by Westmoreland Mall and then Monroeville).

PROS: 
VERY Clean;
Huge food court with appealing dining options;
A ton of stores;
Restrooms are very clean!
Parking is plentiful all around the mall (except if you'd like to park @ the Food Court entrance--that's always a bit tricky with the theater sharing the lot).
Apple Store;
Coach Store;
Sephora... need I say more?         :)

CONS:
n/a
I seriously don't have any complaints about this mall.
